1.how to start mongodb
  C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\bin>mongod.exe --dbpath \Users\hijisuki\mongo-data
  mongo-data is a file made at first for storing data.
  If "waiting for connections on port 27017" appears, it means success

2.start script to connect
  C:\Users\hijisuki\Desktop\node-todo-api\playground>node mongodb-connect.js

